            "category": "Examination",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>The final exam will assess content covered in lectures and required readings from Week 6 to Week 12. The exam will be paper-based and invigilated on campus.</p>\n<p>The exam will consist of 25 multiple-choice questions (MCQs) that require students to apply their knowledge of consumer behaviour to interpret, analyse or respond to marketing problems.</p>\n<p>Preparation for the final exam will be discussed in lectures.</p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
